      • parseQSYSFilePath

        java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> parseQSYSFilePath(java.lang.String input)
                                                            throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Returns the parsed QSYS File path from RPG /COPY format to the individual components
        Parameters:
        input - Takes the following forms
        • libraryname/filename,membername
        • filename,membername
        • membername
        Returns:
        The map will have the components of the path in their own slot using the Static Final Strings MAP_KEY_* as the keys
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
